WEBVTT

00:08.885 --> 00:10.375
(Ship's horn blaring)

00:10.511 --> 00:12.843
(Sonny) I don't get it.

00:12.972 --> 00:16.055
(Annie) I'm saying I need to take
a moment to myself here.

00:16.184 --> 00:18.175
Musically or what?

00:18.311 --> 00:21.519
It's just the music. It's like I said.

00:24.025 --> 00:26.437
Would you rather it was the other way?

00:26.569 --> 00:28.730
That we broke up but kept playing together?

00:28.863 --> 00:31.195
