00:31.324 --> 00:34.361
I need to stretch myself, you know?

00:34.493 --> 00:36.745
l have to play in different styles.

00:36.871 --> 00:38.862
We're not practicing anymore.

00:38.998 --> 00:42.240
— We're not working on arrangements.
— What the fuck, Annie?

00:46.714 --> 00:49.296
