at the end of the day like it's no big deal?

01:12.615 --> 01:15.652
— Sonny, it's no big deal.
- Fuck no.

01:15.785 --> 01:19.824
We play together.
If we don't play together, we aren't together.

01:19.956 --> 01:23.198
- Sonny, please.
— Either you're with me or you're not.

01:32.134 --> 01:34.045
— Get your shit out of my apartment.
— Sonny!

01:34.178 --> 01:36.510
- |...
— Go! Just get your shit and go.

01:39.684 --> 01:41.675
— (Can clatters)
— (Ship's horn blows)

03:26.248 --> 03:28.455
Professor Bernette.

03:28.584 --> 03:30.575
— Mr. Loomis.
— You gonna be late?

