04:55.004 --> 04:57.040
She was a local?

04:57.173 --> 04:59.539
Kate Chopin lived all over Louisiana.

04:59.675 --> 05:02.041
New Orleans, Natchitoches Parish.

05:02.178 --> 05:04.760
